Edit /usr/lib/vxvm/bin/vxroot
	Verify, approx. line 138 the line:
		if [ $? -eq 0 -a -n $bus_drivers ] ;
		should be
		if [ $? -eq 0 -a -n "$bus_drivers" ] ;
		With the quotes around $bus_drivers"

encapsulate root / reboot
	vsdiskadm

re-mirror rootdisk
	vxdg -g rootdg adddisk Disk_1
	vxedit -g rootdg rename Disk_1 rootmirror
	zero out all slices on mirror disk partition table (at least 3 and 4)
	vxdiskadm
		Opt 6
		
Verify SAN is visible to VXVM

